dcterms:description: DanceTrack dataset is designed to be more challenging, featuring targets with similar appearances, severe occlusions, and irregular motions. It contains 40 videos for training, 25 for validation, and 35 for testing.
dcterms:title: DanceTrack

dcterms:description: KITTIMOT dataset contains videos of cars and pedestrians recorded with a camera mounted on top of a car driving through a city. It is challenging due to its lower frame rate of 10 FPS.
dcterms:title: KITTIMOT

dcterms:description: MOT17 is a popular dataset for multi-object tracking, containing 7 training videos and 7 test videos with scenes featuring simple and linear movements of humans.
